Text: Vanguard Mid-Cap Growth ETF (NYSEARCA:VOT) Plans  -  Dividend of $0.30 Tweet  Vanguard Mid-Cap Growth ETF (NYSEARCA:VOT) declared a  -  dividend on Monday, September 16th, Wall Street Journal reports.
